==Latin==
===Etymology===
From [[w:Doric Greek|Doric Greek]] '''[[μαχανά]]''' (''machana'') ([[Ionic Greek]] '''[[μηχανή]]''' ''[[mechane]]'') "machine, tool", from [[μάχος]], [[μήχος]] (''machos'', ''mechos'') "device, assistance, way".


